OrdersGui
=========

Silverlight GUI for SLOM
This project is based on the MVVM Light Toolkit v4.1 by Laurent Bugnion ([info](http://www.galasoft.ch/mvvm/))

##Requisites##

- Silverlight 5
- .NET 4.5
- MvvmLight 4.1 for SL5
